name: WARP HEN #12 - Prototype Set
description:
I have been wanting to create a collectible series i could drop on HEN similar to my WARP PUNKS series so I took the warp punk art concept and an outline of an actual HEN and created WARP HENS!! 
This is the initial Prototype run of 20 1/1 Warp Hens 
If the interest is there and these sell out I intend to do an official much larger run.
